                    <head>Breviary (fragmented)</head>
                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc form="codex">
                            <supportDesc>
                                <extent>
                                    <measure type="leftFlyleaves" unit="folios"/>
                                    <measure type="rightFlyleaves" unit="folios"/>
                                </extent>
                                <foliation>Modern foliation in pencil, 1-150, 151 (corrected from 150), 152-160, 161 (corrected from 160), 162-166, 167A, 167B, 168-185. There is a second modern foliation in pencil in the lower left corner and a third in the bottom margin. Erroneous foliation has been corrected, see e.g. <locus from="152r" to="152r" scheme="folios"/> and <locus from="177r" to="177r" scheme="folios"/>.</foliation>
                                <collation>
                                    <formula>1(10, leaves 1-6 and 10 replaced), 2(10), 3(12, leaves 1-11 replaced), 4(10), 5(6), 6(4, leaves 1-2 replaced), 7-18(10), 19(10, leaves 8-10 replaced), 20(10, leaves 5-10 replaced), 21(10 + 1, leaves 2 and 7 replaced), 22(2), 23(12, leaf 12 replaced). </formula>
                                    <p>Replaced leaves are not inserted in the right place, see further under Contents. Originally, the manuscript was probably made up of quires of ten leaves, four paper bifolia around one inner parchment bifolium. Fourteen such quires are still extant. <ref target="https://vceditor.library.upenn.edu/project/682c6378f060c60001cc1d96/viewOnly">VisColl collation</ref>
                                    </p>
                                    <catchwords>Catchwords still extant. <locus from="24v" to="24v" scheme="folios"/> (not in agreement with the following page); <locus from="32v" to="32v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="42v" to="42v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="62v" to="62v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="72v" to="72v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="82v" to="82v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="92v" to="92v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="102v" to="102v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="112v" to="112v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="132v" to="132v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="142v" to="142v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="152v" to="152v" scheme="folios"/>. </catchwords>
                                </collation>
                            </supportDesc>
