                            <additions>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="1r" to="172v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Corrections and minor additions throughout in different contemporary hands, see e.g. <locus from="22r" to="22v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="76r" to="76r" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="123r" to="123r" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="137v" to="137v" scheme="folios"/>.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="14v" to="14v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Additions by two different hands. The first on how to procede if there are more than twenty-five sundays after Trinity, the second on how to celebrate the Octave for St Andrew.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="172v" to="172v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Text for the second nocturn added in the lower part of the page.</note>
                                </p>
                            </additions>
                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in brown ink. Rubrics in red. Capitals touched in red. <locus from="178r" to="185v" scheme="folios"/>: Red not used </p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p>Plain initials over two lines in red, some in black, e.g. <locus from="10r" to="10r" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="169r" to="169v" scheme="folios"/>, some with light flourishing in red or brown, e.g. <locus from="10r" to="10r" scheme="folios"/>
                                        <locus from="116v" to="116v" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="177v" to="177v" scheme="folios"/>. A few hanging <quote>I</quote>s and <quote>P</quote>s and <quote>F</quote>s with descenders along the column, e.g. <locus from="148r" to="148r" scheme="folios"/>, with flourishing <locus from="49v" to="49v" scheme="folios"/>. <locus from="36v" to="36v" scheme="folios"/>: Plain initial <quote>I</quote> in red over three lines with flourishing extending above and below along the column. <locus from="117r" to="119r" scheme="folios"/>: Four plain initials in both black and red with flourishing.</p>
                                </decoNote>
